title: Preserving Fashion's Past, Present, Future with Conservator Sarah Scaturro
itunes:title: Preserving Fashion's Past, Present, Future with Conservator Sarah Scaturro
description:
Sarah Scaturro, Chief Conservator at the Cleveland Museum of Art, takes us behind the seams of museums to talk about the intricate and fascinating job of fashion conservation. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
